	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p><addressee>Messers Leeser</addressee> &#38;<lb/> <addressee>Rev Dr Bondi</addressee></p>
				<p>Sirs.&#8212;the address I sent<lb/> to you &#38; <add>&#63;</add> it down<lb/> solely for the object of<lb/> some instruction on<lb/> the inspiration Holy<lb/> <add>&#63;</add>.  I asked out the<lb/> sincerity of my heart<lb/> and well wisher of<lb/> your people&#44; I have<lb/> wrote two letters to<lb/> <add>&#63;</add> one of them<lb/> <sic>resently</sic> issue I wrote<lb/> to you&#44; for a <add>&#63;</add><lb/> or sample of your <add>&#63;</add><lb/> in the Editorial sphere<lb/> of Publications a No of the<lb/> Israelite a Periodical.<lb/>  I have a sample of your<lb/> No. 7.  It was sent to me<lb/> by the Ed. &#38; <sic>Propritor</sic> of the</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p><sic>Biblicle</sic> Expositor<lb/> Printed now at <add>&#63;</add> <placeName>Detr<lb/>oit Mich</placeName> I take it</p>
				<p>My Faith is in the gos<lb/>pel of our savior <persName>Jesus<lb/> Christ</persName> the promised<lb/> messiah the Prince of Peace&#59;<lb/> to Reign on <persName>Davids</persName> Royal<lb/> Throne or King of <placeName>Israel</placeName><lb/> Personally in <placeName>Jerusalem</placeName><lb/> <placeName><sic>Palistine</sic></placeName>&#44; <placeName>Asia Minor</placeName>&#44;<lb/> in <placeName>Turkey</placeName>.  When He<lb/> comes He comes in King<lb/>dom In a Mighty Chariot<lb/> The city of the <placeName>New Jerusa<lb/>lem</placeName>&#59; the second one.<lb/>  The New Temple will<lb/> be in it and a New<lb/> Throne in it.  His Domain<lb/> will be over the whole<lb/> earth and <add>&#63;</add> and<lb/> seas.  <add>&#63;</add> an everlasting<lb/> one as eternity.</p>
				<p>My Faith is of His Now to be<lb/> His <add>&#63;</add> one at time of His Birth</p>
			<pb n="3"/>
				<p>was His first Advent.  <add>&#63;</add><lb/> Acts 1 <add>&#63;</add> and 12 vs <persName>Zach</persName><lb/> <add>&#63;</add> &#38;c so likewise my Faith<lb/> is of the Restoration of the<lb/> whole House of <placeName>Israel</placeName> to the<lb/> hand of their Fathers <add>&#63;</add><lb/> In the days <persName>Adam</persName> it was<lb/> <sic>was</sic> called <placeName>Eden</placeName> Now <placeName>Palis<lb/>tine</placeName>.</p>
				<p>If you will answer my<lb/> Former letter namely of<lb/> I wrote it will oblige me<lb/> much&#44; or give your opin<lb/>ion on them.</p>
				<p>Return them to me after<lb/> the same manner as I<lb/> write to you not in man<lb/>ner as I proposed.</p>
				<p>I wish not for controversy<lb/> <add>&#63;</add> in my <add>&#63;</add> write&#45;ing in<lb/> the way I have to you<lb/> nor for reputation.<lb/>  I may write to you occa<add>&#63;</add>ly<lb/> if of what I have is excerpted<lb/> I am a gentile and am a poor</p>
			<pb n="4"/>
				<p>and no Family &#38; live in a house<add>&#63;</add> alone &#38;<lb/> have had a wife but she is<lb/> Dead and was of the same<lb/> Faith of myself she died <date>1850</date><lb/> what I may hereafter write<lb/> upon will be  the <sic>Prophecys</sic><lb/> of Holy writ&#44; and History of<lb/> past Present and Future<lb/> giving my views of them<lb/> and Faith As I under<lb/>stand them they may be<lb/> of some importance to you<lb/> I am a professional man<lb/> a Botanic Doctor Reduced<lb/> by <add>&#63;</add> of Prosperity by False<lb/> Hearted men and their<lb/> writing of such as Mortg<add>&#63;</add><lb/>ages on Landed Property such<add>&#63;</add><lb/> as Real Estate.</p>
				<p>I have read two <add>&#63;</add><lb/> of three <sic>peices</sic> of latter part of<lb/> the Occident and I like them<lb/> much and intend on Reading<lb/> it through.  <add>&#63;</add><lb/> 18th <add>&#63;</add> <persName>L. Dale. D. B.</persName><lb/> I am a man 61 years old<lb/> in 62nd year.</p>
		</body>
